Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Specialist Peter J. Loretto, Jr. Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Specialist Peter J. Loretto, Jr. Memorial Bridge" in the town of Eden, county of Erie.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Specialist Peter J. Loretto, Jr. Memorial Bridge"
